query: the films that share the directors with the film [Catch Me If You Can] were in which languages
generated_query:
MATCH (m:Movie {name: "Catch Me If You Can"})-[:DIRECTED_BY]->(d:Director)<-[:DIRECTED_BY]-(other:Movie)-[:IN_LANGUAGE]->(l:Language)
RETURN DISTINCT l.name

query: which holds films for the director of [Written on the Wind]
target_query: Sandra Dee|Charles Coburn|Cornel Wilde|John Gavin|Warren William|Susan Kohner|Joan Bennett|Fred MacMurray|Barbara Stanwyck|Don Ameche|Jane Wyman|Rochelle Hudson|Boris Karloff|Patricia Knight|Robert Cummings|Rock Hudson|Lucille Ball|Claudette Colbert|Lana Turner|George Sanders
generated_query:
MATCH (m:Movie)-[:DIRECTED_BY]->(d:Director) 
WHERE m.name = "Written on the Wind" 
WITH d 
MATCH (m2:Movie)-[:DIRECTED_BY]->(d) 
RETURN m2.name
